      "acceptanceCriteria": "CFD solver must have documented verification tests and version-controlled release notes.",
      "rationale": "ANSYS Fluent 2022R2 is used. Vendor-supplied verification suite passes all relevant benchmark cases. Version control and release notes archived in project repository. Achieved level exceeds MRL 2 requirement."
