      "acceptanceCriteria": "Not required at MRL 2 for this factor.",
      "rationale": "Test sample characterization beyond standard ASTM F1841 protocol is not required at Model Risk Level 2 for this application. The validation experiments used fresh ovine blood within the ASTM-specified hematocrit range (35–45%). Detailed sample-to-sample variability analysis is scoped out at this risk level."
    },
    {
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
      "factorType": "Equivalency of input parameters",
      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
