      "rationale": "Formal equivalency mapping between validation experiment input parameters and COU input parameters is not required at MRL 2. The operating conditions used in validation (flow rates, rotational speeds, fluid temperature) are nominally consistent with the COU operating envelope. No systematic parameter equivalency analysis is documented, which is acceptable at this risk level."
    }
